name: Memory Road
description: this is a picture of a train from my childhood. i rode this train many times growing up, and when i got a bit older- i drove it as it was at my first job. this train now sits in abandoned for the past 15 years in a garage on the grounds. this was a very nostalgic moment for me to capture now as an adult going back there to see it all. very memorable and maybe the most notable and nostalgic part of the whole place
